tool.name: ModifySelectedSite

param.name: siteid
param.dialogReference: The new code for the selected water quality points.

param.name: shp_file
param.displayname: WQ points to change site code

tool.summary:
Changes the assigned site for a selection of water quality records.

This tool was designed to work on a selection - use the interactive selection method to pick out the water quality points that you want to modify. Make sure that all the features selected are the ones that you meant to modify.
